---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Compliance-Ready Managed IT for Regulated Firms
description: IronGate delivers managed IT, cybersecurity, and compliance support built for healthcare, legal, and financial firms.
---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction">
  <div>
    <span class="pill">HIPAA &middot; SOC 2 &middot; compliance-ready IT</span>
    <h1 class="display-1">IT that keeps regulated business running.</h1>
    <p class="lead">IronGate delivers managed IT, cybersecurity, and compliance support built for healthcare, legal, and financial firms &mdash; so downtime, audits, and breaches never slow you down.</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact/">Book a free consult</a>
      <a class="btn btn--outline" href="/contact/?assessment=1">Get a security assessment</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__stats">
      {% for stat in site.heroStats %}
        {% if not loop.first %}<div class="hero__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>{% endif %}
        <div>
          <div class="hero__stat-value">{{ stat.value }}</div>
          <div class="hero__stat-label">{{ stat.label }}</div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% if site.images.hero %}
  <img class="photo photo--hero" src="{{ site.images.hero }}" alt="The IronGate team at work">
  {% else %}
  <div class="img-placeholder img-placeholder--hero" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder for a photo of the IronGate IT team">
    <span>[ hero photo &mdash; IT team / server room ]</span>
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</section>

{% if site.sections.certifications %}
<section class="badge-strip" aria-label="Partners and certifications">
  <span class="badge-strip__label">Partners &amp; certifications</span>
  {% for cert in certifications.items %}
    <span class="badge-strip__item">{{ cert.name }}</span>
  {% endfor %}
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if site.sections.services %}
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
  <div class="section-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">What we do</p>
    <h2 id="services-heading" class="display-2">A full IT department, managed for you</h2>
    <p>Seven core services, one accountable team, flat monthly pricing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-3">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M8 20h8M12 16v4"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#managed" style="color:inherit">Managed IT Services</a></h3>
      <p>24/7 monitoring, help desk, and proactive maintenance so problems are solved before you notice them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 18a4 4 0 1 1 .5-7.97A6 6 0 0 1 18 8a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 .5 8.97z"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#cloud" style="color:inherit">Cloud Computing</a></h3>
      <p>Migrate, host, and scale in the cloud with secure access for a distributed, compliant workforce.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 3l8 3v6c0 4.5-3.4 7.8-8 9-4.6-1.2-8-4.5-8-9V6z"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#network" style="color:inherit">Network Security</a></h3>
      <p>Firewalls, endpoint protection, and threat detection tuned to your budget and risk profile.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><ellipse cx="12" cy="6" rx="7" ry="3"/><path d="M5 6v12c0 1.7 3.1 3 7 3s7-1.3 7-3V6"/><path d="M5 12c0 1.7 3.1 3 7 3s7-1.3 7-3"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#backup" style="color:inherit">Data Backup &amp; Recovery</a></h3>
      <p>Automated offsite backups and tested recovery plans that get you running again in minutes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 20c0-3.3 3.6-5 8-5s8 1.7 8 5"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#remote" style="color:inherit">Remote IT Support</a></h3>
      <p>Fast remote help desk resolution for on-site, hybrid, and fully remote teams &mdash; wherever they work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 3l8 3v6c0 4.5-3.4 7.8-8 9-4.6-1.2-8-4.5-8-9V6z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#compliance" style="color:inherit">Cybersecurity &amp; Compliance</a></h3>
      <p>HIPAA, SOC 2, and PCI readiness with audits, staff training, and documented policies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-chip" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2l2 5-2.5 1.5a12 12 0 0 0 5 5L14 12l5 2v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2C9.8 18 4 12.2 4 5z"/></svg></div>
      <h3><a href="/services/#voip" style="color:inherit">VoIP &amp; Phone Systems</a></h3>
      <p>Modern cloud phone systems with call routing, voicemail-to-email, and mobile apps.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card card--dashed">
      <h3>Not sure what you need?</h3>
      <p>Book a 30-minute consult and we'll map your risks and gaps.</p>
      <a class="text-link" href="/contact/">Book a consult &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="card card--navy">
      <div class="card__big">Flat rate.</div>
      <div class="card__big card__big--teal">No surprises.</div>
      <p>Predictable monthly billing that scales with your headcount, never your incidents.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if site.sections.industries %}
<section class="section section--navy" id="industries" aria-labelledby="industries-heading">
  <div class="section-head">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Who we serve</p>
    <h2 id="industries-heading" class="display-2">Built for industries that can't afford to fail an audit</h2>
  </div>
  {% set indCount = industries.items | length %}
  <div class="grid-industries{% if indCount <= 4 %} grid-industries--{{ indCount }}{% endif %}">
    {% for ind in industries.items %}
    <div class="industry-card">
      <div class="industry-card__index">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }} / {{ ind.label }}</div>
      <h3>{{ ind.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ ind.body }}</p>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if site.sections.testimonials %}
<section class="section section--mist" aria-labelledby="testimonials-heading">
  <div class="section-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">Client stories</p>
    <h2 id="testimonials-heading" class="display-2">Trusted by teams who can't go dark</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-2">
    {% for t in testimonials.items %}
    <figure class="quote-card">
      <blockquote>
        <p>&ldquo;{{ t.quote }}&rdquo;</p>
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption>
        <div class="quote-card__avatar" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="quote-card__name">{{ t.name }}</div>
          <div class="quote-card__role">{{ t.role }}</div>
        </div>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if site.sections.news %}
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="news-heading">
  <div class="news-header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Resources</p>
      <h2 id="news-heading" class="display-2" style="font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,32px)">Security news &amp; guidance</h2>
    </div>
    <a class="text-link" href="/resources/">View all articles &rarr;</a>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-3">
    {% for item in news | limit(3) %}
    <article class="news-card">
      <div class="news-card__thumb news-card__thumb--{{ item.slug }}" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="news-card__wordmark">{{ item.source }}<span>.</span></div>
        <div class="news-card__tagline">{{ item.tagline }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="news-card__body">
        <div class="news-card__date">{{ item.date | newsDate }} &middot; {{ item.source }}</div>
        <h3><a href="{{ item.link }}" rel="noopener external" target="_blank">{{ item.title }}<span style="position:absolute;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;clip:rect(0 0 0 0);"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a></h3>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% else %}
    <p style="color:var(--slate-500)">Fresh security headlines are being gathered &mdash; check back shortly.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% include "partials/cta.njk" %}
